# Godot 4+ ignores.
#
# The import cache under .godot/ is INTENTIONALLY tracked so a fresh clone or a
# GitHub source-zip opens and runs without waiting for the editor to reimport
# every asset. Only the volatile, machine-/GPU-specific parts are ignored:
#   - editor/       per-user editor layout, recent files, last-opened scene
#   - shader_cache/ compiled shaders, regenerated per GPU/driver at runtime
# If you change an asset's import settings, re-commit the updated .godot/imported
# so downloads stay in sync.
.godot/editor/
.godot/shader_cache/
/android/
